<section id="get-your-voice-heard" class="block-pad">
    <div class="container container--1200">

            <header class="container u--center">
                <h2 class="h1">Get your voice heard</h2>
                    <div class="large">
                        <p>Let us know how the outbreak is impacting your business</p>
                    </div>
                <hr class="grad">
                <br>
                <br>
            </header>

        <div class="flex-row">

                <div>
                    <div>
                        <p><span>Business needs to see real and decisive action from the government in order to weather this storm. The CBI will help to establish what that action must look like, and we will take your suggestions directly to the heart of government to make sure their measures are timely and effective. If you’d like to contribute and get your voice heard, please share your thoughts and experiences with us. Every business’ view matters.</span><br /><span> </span><br /><span>You can also reach out and ask us any questions via our dedicated COVID-19 inbox: </span><a rel="noopener" href="mailto:coronavirussupport@cbi.org.uk" target="_blank">coronavirussupport@cbi.org.uk</a></p>
<p>If you'd like your business' experiences to be reflected in our economic surveys, <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.cbi.org.uk/what-we-do/economic-surveys/" target="_blank">you can take part here</a>. Your response will provide invaluable insight into how the coronavirus outbreak has affected industries and the wider UK economy.</p>
                    </div>
